# Category Requests
###################

### Create Category
POST http://localhost:3000/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "category to delete" 
}

### Get All Categories
GET http://localhost:3000/categories

### Get Cateogory by Id
GET http://localhost:3000/categories/v1t8y8qoc64068dvqxmdqxzm

