PUT http://localhost:3000/categories/v1t8y8qoc64068dvqxmdqxzm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated the name using VSCode Rest Client"
}

### Delete Category by Id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/categories/q64hnv1z2t8e5uxbxoqfupqn

